        <abstract> 
<p>Mentions a discussion of man by Isidore Geoffroy Saint-Hilaire in his <hi rend="italic">Histoire naturelle générale</hi> [1854–62].</p>  
<p>Mentions a book by Friedrich Rolle [<hi rend="italic">Ch. Darwin’s Lehre von der Entstehung der Arten</hi> (1863)].</p> 
            <p>Cites evolutionary statements on elephants by Hugh Falconer and notes Falconer’s objection to natural selection.</p>
        </abstract>
